Definition.WordDefinition:
CoCo
<computer> The {Tandy} Color Computer with a Motorola {MC6809E} {CPU}. The {Dragon} is a CoCo clone. The CoCo was as powerful as the {IBM XT} at the time it was made, and could run {OS-9}.
